<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: right;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" style="" size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" style="" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><span lang="en-GB" style="text-align: start; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><div style="margin: 0px;"><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">I would like to draw your attention to the attached, updated IT Acceptable Use policy for our students.&nbsp; &nbsp;We are sharing this with students&nbsp; from Year 5 and above tomorrow and I would be grateful for your support in helping to reenforce the importance of safe and appropriate use of electronic devices.&nbsp; &nbsp;I have spoken to some year groups already and tutors will go through our expectations with the children.</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">Whilst we accept and indeed embrace technology as a means to enhance our children's education, we also recognise that improper use of electronic devices,&nbsp; and social media can be extremely harmful, hurtful or distressing.&nbsp; &nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">It is vital that we act together as a community to uphold this policy so as to protect our children from the potentially negative consequences of IT.&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">Should you have any queries or wish to discuss this with us, please do talk to a member of&nbsp; SLT.&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">Kind regards,&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><div><br></div><div dir="ltr" class="m_-9140481519742757712gmail_signature" data-smartmail="gmail_signature"><div dir="ltr"><div><b>Tor Del Federico</b></div><div>Principal</div></div></div></div><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><br></div></font></span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><font size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" style="">The British School Yangon</font></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" size="2">www.britishschoolyangon.org</font></p></div></div>]]></td>
